[h1]What are Creature Sizes?[/h1]
Using identical rules for a sparrow and a bison would make little sense, so this system differentiates between creatures of different sizes. This is mostly based on vibes â€“ there are no hard thresholds since it would be impossible to take everything from height to density into consideration.
